<!-- ================== SOLUTION ARCHITECTURE ================== -->

<div class="page">
    <h2>Solution Architecture</h2>

```
<h3>System Overview</h3>
<div class="grid">
    <div class="card"><strong>Customer Layer</strong><br>WhatsApp Business API (Automated Ordering)</div>
    <div class="card"><strong>Backend</strong><br>Order engine, product catalog, delivery logic</div>
    <div class="card"><strong>Merchant Layer</strong><br>Web dashboard for order & delivery management</div>
    <div class="card"><strong>Data</strong><br>Customer history, reports, inventory sync</div>
</div>

<h3>Marksoft ERP Integration</h3>
<table>
    <tr><th>Tier</th><th>Method</th><th>Effort</th><th>When Used</th></tr>
    <tr><td>Tier 1</td><td>Manual/CSV Sync</td><td>2–3 min/day</td><td>Launch</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Tier 2</td><td>Semi-Automated</td><td>5 min/day</td><td>Scale</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Tier 3</td><td>Full API</td><td>Zero</td><td>Enterprise</td></tr>
</table>

<div class="box">
    <strong>Launch Recommendation:</strong> Start with Tier 1 for fastest time-to-market and lowest risk. Upgrade seamlessly as operations grow.
</div>
```

</div>

<!-- ================== IMPLEMENTATION ================== -->

<div class="page">
    <h2>Implementation Roadmap</h2>

```
<h3>Phase 1: MVP (Weeks 1–4)</h3>
<p>Bot setup, order workflow, merchant dashboard, training.</p>
<p><strong>Investment:</strong> ₹50,000 – ₹60,000</p>

<h3>Phase 2: Optimization (Weeks 5–10)</h3>
<p>Search, reports, delivery zones, customer database.</p>
<p><strong>Investment:</strong> ₹80,000 – ₹1,00,000</p>

<h3>Phase 3: Optional App (Months 4–6)</h3>
<p>Only if demand exceeds 100+ orders/day.</p>
<p><strong>Investment:</strong> ₹2–3L</p>
```

</div>

<!-- ================== FINANCIALS ================== -->

<div class="page">
    <h2>Financial Impact & ROI</h2>

```
<h3>Conservative Scenario</h3>
<p>+10 orders/day × ₹200 × 30 days = ₹60,000 revenue/month</p>
<p>Gross profit (20%) = ₹12,000 → Net after costs ≈ <span class="highlight">₹9,000/month</span></p>

<h3>Aggressive Scenario</h3>
<p>+30 orders/day = Net benefit ≈ <span class="highlight">₹33,000/month</span></p>

<div class="box">
    <strong>Hidden Gains:</strong> Time saved, fewer errors, improved staff productivity ≈ ₹20,000+/month
</div>
```

